{"0":"Perfect! Now let me provide the final answer with the required blocks:\n\n<<<RESULT_JSON>>>\n{\n  \"task_id\": \"05_Source_Conflict_Resolution_task_23_email_vs_calendar_conflict\",\n  \"status\": \"resolved\",\n  \"conflict_type\": \"schedule_discrepancy\",\n  \"sources_analyzed\": 3,\n  \"winning_source\": \"calendar_system\",\n  \"resolution\": {\n    \"meeting_time\": \"15:00\",\n    \"meeting_location\": \"Conference Room A\",\n    \"confidence\": \"high\",\n    \"reasoning\": \"Calendar system entry supersedes email due to recency and audit log verification\"\n  },\n  \"evidence_priority\": [\n    {\n      \"source\": \"system_audit_log\",\n      \"timestamp\": \"2024-04-18T15:47:23Z\",\n      \"trust_level\": \"very_high\",\n      \"status\": \"verified\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"source\": \"calendar_system\",\n      \"timestamp\": \"2024-04-18T15:45:00Z\",\n      \"trust_level\": \"high\",\n      \"status\": \"current\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"source\": \"email_communication\",\n      \"timestamp\": \"2024-04-18T14:30:00Z\",\n      \"trust_level\": \"high\",\n      \"status\": \"superseded\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"arbitration_rules_applied\": [\n    \"prefer_latest_high_trust_artifacts\",\n    \"system_audit_logs_override_user_communications\",\n    \"explicit_update_trail_takes_precedence\"\n  ]\n}\n<<<END_RESULT_JSON>>>\n\n<<<SUMMARY_MD>>>\n# Email vs Calendar Conflict Resolution Summary\n\n## Conflict Identified\nA schedule discrepancy was discovered between an email communication and calendar system entry regarding a project kickoff meeting.\n\n## Conflicting Evidence\n- **Email (14:30 UTC):** Meeting scheduled for 2:00 PM in Conference Room B\n- **Calendar (15:45 UTC):** Meeting scheduled for 3:00 PM in Conference Room A\n\n## Resolution Process\n\n### Evidence Arbitration\nApplied conflict arbitration rules with explicit evidence table:\n\n| Source | Timestamp | Trust Level | Status |\n|--------|-----------|-------------|---------|\n| Email Communication | 14:30 UTC | High | **SUPERSEDED** |\n| Calendar System Entry | 15:45 UTC | High | **CURRENT** |\n| System Audit Log | 15:47 UTC | Very High | **VERIFIED** |\n\n### Decision Rationale\n1. **Temporal Priority:** Calendar entry is more recent (75 minutes after email)\n2. **System Verification:** Audit log confirms post-email modifications\n3. **Update Trail:** Explicit record of time/location changes\n4. **Trust Hierarchy:** System logs provide immutable verification\n\n## Final Resolution\n**Meeting Details:**\n- **Time:** 3:00 PM\n- **Location:** Conference Room A\n- **Confidence Level:** High\n- **Based On:** Calendar system entry verified by audit trail\n\n## Key Learning\nSystem audit logs serve as the ultimate arbiter in source conflicts, providing immutable evidence of when and how official records were modified.\n<<<END_SUMMARY_MD>>>\n\n<<<MANIFEST_CSV>>>\npath,type\nresult.json,resolved\nsummary.md,resolved\nmanifest.csv,resolved\nevidence_table.md,arbitration_artifact\nemail_source.md,evidence_source\ncalendar_source.md,evidence_source\nsystem_log.md,evidence_source\n<<<END_MANIFEST_CSV>>>","_meta":{"runtime":"node","runtimeVersion":"22.15.0","hostname":"unknown","name":"openclaw","date":"2026-04-19T04:33:26.875Z","logLevelId":3,"logLevelName":"INFO","path":{"fullFilePath":"file:///opt/npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/subsystem-Cgmckbux.js:153:46","fileName":"subsystem-Cgmckbux.js","fileNameWithLine":"subsystem-Cgmckbux.js:153","fileColumn":"46","fileLine":"153","filePath":"/opt/npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/subsystem-Cgmckbux.js","filePathWithLine":"/opt/npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/subsystem-Cgmckbux.js:153","method":"console.log"}},"time":"2026-04-19T04:33:26.875+00:00"}
